    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>建立你自己的商业帝国！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Business Simulator 2026</strong> 是一款商业模拟游戏，您将从零开始，成长为全球巨头。做出战略决策，发展您的公司，克服财务挑战，超越竞争对手！您将培养成为商业世界领导者所需的所有技能。掌握营销、生产和管理流程，抓住机遇并有效管理风险。 <br><br><strong>公司成立</strong>：<br>建立您的公司，迈出商业世界的第一步。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098060/extras/dc1809263219abf3f97db4dc7f317352.poster.avif?t=1771139861\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098060/extras/dc1809263219abf3f97db4dc7f317352.webm?t=1771139861\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098060/extras/dc1809263219abf3f97db4dc7f317352.mp4?t=1771139861\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>业务选择：通过策略脱颖而出！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >决定在哪个行业运营。根据市场分析和竞争状况制定您的商业计划。选择正确的行业是成功的第一步！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098060/extras/8afaf0cf589f22da2d8929044d13b347.poster.avif?t=1771139861\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098060/extras/8afaf0cf589f22da2d8929044d13b347.webm?t=1771139861\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098060/extras/8afaf0cf589f22da2d8929044d13b347.mp4?t=1771139861\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>生产管理</strong>：<br>分析您的产品，推向市场，满足需求！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098060/extras/f7c422b44194cbcc37d5f973f279cccb.poster.avif?t=1771139861\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098060/extras/f7c422b44194cbcc37d5f973f279cccb.webm?t=1771139861\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098060/extras/f7c422b44194cbcc37d5f973f279cccb.mp4?t=1771139861\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>店铺扩展与自动化：持续收入来源</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >扩展您的店铺，雇用更多员工以实现业务自动化。扩大您的业务，享受持续收入。通过战略性投资将您的店铺变成赚钱机器！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098060/extras/aff15e75ced85206265f552435e4b1ac.poster.avif?t=1771139861\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098060/extras/aff15e75ced85206265f552435e4b1ac.webm?t=1771139861\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098060/extras/aff15e75ced85206265f552435e4b1ac.mp4?t=1771139861\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>您决定通向顶峰的道路</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一个决定都将塑造您公司的未来。制定战略，抓住机遇，掌握商业世界的复杂动态，击败竞争对手！</p>",
